OL,6,FA man dragged his former partner
OL,7,Facross the ground alongside a moving
OL,8,Fcar - after she refused to add him on
OL,9,FFacebook.
OL,11,FChristopher Dacre, 38, got angry when
OL,12,Fthe mother of his children told him
OL,13,Fshe did not want to be in a
OL,14,Frelationship on 7 September 2023.
OL,16,FDacre, of Heathfield Drive, Preston,
OL,17,Fturned up to her house threatening to
OL,18,Fwake the children if she did not let
OL,19,Fhim in.
