OL,3,CMan dragged former partner alongside
OL,4,Cmoving car after Facebook snub
OL,6,FHe then turned up the next morning
OL,7,Fwhere he assaulted her, taking her
OL,8,Fphone and keys and pushing to the
OL,9,Fground and driving whilst she was
OL,10,Fhanging out of the car door, Preston
OL,11,FCrown Court was told.
OL,13,FDacre originally pleaded not guilty to
OL,14,Fdangerous driving and common assault,
OL,15,Fbut later changed his plea.
OL,17,FHe received a 15 month sentence,
OL,18,Fsuspended for 18 months, 120 hours of
OL,19,Fcommunity service and a 12-month
OL,20,Fdriving ban.
