OL,6,FHe has also been given a five-year
OL,7,Frestraining order.
OL,9,FDuring the trial, the court heard how
OL,10,Fone of the children had become
OL,11,Fseverely distressed during the attack,
OL,12,Fshouting to a neighbour "my mummy my
OL,13,Fdaddy."
OL,15,FThe victim said the attack has caused
OL,16,Fher to take leave from work, start
OL,17,Ftaking antidepressants and move home
OL,18,Fout of fear.
